Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:01.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:02.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you ignore my text yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:05.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, wasn't feeling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, every day,\Nyou're like, "What'cha doin'?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:10.37,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:15.05,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki and I have been\Ndating for nearly a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:20.30,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't even kissed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:22.18,sign_1891_9_Point_Blank_Rela,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Point-Blank Relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:25.16,Default,Nagoya curls,0000,0000,0000,,What? You still haven't kissed, Kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:27.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's only been a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:28.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:29.98,Default,Nagoya curls,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit late?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.18,Default,Nagoya curls,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't Chiaki-kun said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, he's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was a huge dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:40.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You poop tanker!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:42.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I poop?! Everyone poops!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're so immature!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.90,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:48.10,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,it feels more like\Nwe're siblings than dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:53.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chiaki, we get along well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! I've been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're definitely in sync, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:00.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you satisfied with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:05.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:06.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:11.09,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm not, but can't\Nwe be closer? Skinship-wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:12.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:13.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to rumble?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:16.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:18.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I meant relationship-type stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You could have said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:21.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a toy to you, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to be funny, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:28.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What about, like, kissing and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't even dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:34.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing for me, too,\Nbut we're in a rel—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:35.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:39.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to waste\Nyour time with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a crush or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We {\i1}are{\i0} dating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:43.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, since when are we dating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed to you last spring, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Coming home from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:00.91,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, I like you, Chiaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.03,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I like you more, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I thought that was a comedy bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something wasn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.27,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't even try to hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But you were always, like, my best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe you were embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I was okay with that, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,since you were always right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we've always been close
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,but never touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:31.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Because, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I've been texting you nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:40.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,and smacking you like we're that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hook up properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What, is this another bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought about being your boyfriend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't tell how you felt,\Nso I kept quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:55.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's date for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text you like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, text me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can I smack you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, smack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.17,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:12.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So let's keep doing comedy bits, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.21,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I confessed to my crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.57,sign_6305_86_I_ll_Kill_Senpai,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}I'll Kill Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.57,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:26.88,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.27,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Going home, Matsuura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What about club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you skipping? Hiuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:36.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabotage? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Skipping? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:41.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Katori-senpai, I'm not feeling well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:44.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You had a sad look on your face.\NI was sure you were heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I nailed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, should I not have asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.01,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But you worked up the courage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.23,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You have an absolutely dazzling\Nlook on your face right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you messing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.49,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.03,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:19.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying in here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:31.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's really {\i1}yourself{\i0}\Nyou want to hit, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you feel better\Nafter hitting me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.27,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai was doing that on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.61,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I feel grateful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you even care so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your senpai. You're my kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good, now you can make it to club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.88,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's annoying, but he's\Na nice guy at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.16,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But he's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It gets lonely without our local idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.84,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}So{\i1} annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't fallen for me, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:16.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm such a hottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:18.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:19.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:22.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Am I badass? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:30.00,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My crush called me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go for lunch sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? With me? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank you\Nfor helping me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Am I imposing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.17,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll see you on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.58,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why is such a cute girl\Nasking out an uggo like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.23,sign_9955_156_Love_Is_Derpy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Love Is Derpy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.78,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get here too early?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:10.09,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've secretly been in love\Nwith this girl on my bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.82,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I never had the courage to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.35,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.37,Flashback_Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A groper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.21,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.37,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where a coinkydink, Kurihara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.54,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-How's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.88,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, wh-what's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:29.20,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I totally creeped her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought she'd want to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.85,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is she actually coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.88,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there no way she'd invite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.60,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, it was all in my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.29,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Heungh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:39.85,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Heungh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.29,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.18,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Um, please stop staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not staring at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're cute or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:51.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No! I did! I {\i1}do{\i0} think\Nyou're cute, but your outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, your outfit's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, not just your outfit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yamane-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:55.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What should we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.86,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:01.31,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't go too pricey, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.62,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe somewhere cheap, quick, and tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then how about soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's a standing soba stall right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.55,sign_11714_193_Soba_Udon,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Soba     Udon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:10.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,May I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.71,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:19.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Should we order fountain drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine, I'll go home\Nright after we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that I want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to be with you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that was creepy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry, I'll go home right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:40.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'd actually noticed you\Non the bus every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You give your seat up\Nfor seniors all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to do good when I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,because, y'know, I'm a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But when you helped me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to remind you about that awfulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.06,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.05,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She invited me out, and I'm ruining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're so funny, Yamane-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:06.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my face, right? I get that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:12.32,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Maybe for the Heian Period,\Nbut this is the 21st century.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.38,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is she kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.68,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe I just look like a dorky mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:21.75,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.41,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.71,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why the serious face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.91,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{そんな}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.62,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{マジ？！}Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.39,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.85,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, no way this could happen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.54,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{だまされるな}She's deceiving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.33,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{期待するな}Don't get your hopes up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.92,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've been getting ignored by girls for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.38,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.13,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{いやいやいや}No way no way no way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.42,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:28.85,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get your hopes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.84,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{もし本当だったら}What if she's serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:29.84,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.49,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.84,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{まだ心の準備が}I'm not prepared for this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:29.84,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.81,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret getting your hopes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.72,sign_13723_244__Badger_Badger_M,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{どーまんせー} {\c&HD466C5&\3c&H623C61&}Badger Badger Mushroom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.72,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{え？何なの} Why does she look so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.72,sign_13477_222_Why_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{こっちは何もない} Nothing to see here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.72,sign_13723_247__Don_t_get_your_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{期待するな！} {\c&H372DD1&\3c&H4B3B81&\fs26}Don't get your hopes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.24,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But what if she's serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.20,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:36.71,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.18,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm not prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:38.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Go out with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:42.93,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fountain drink, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.44,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The person on cleanup duty went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.94,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:51.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Takano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.93,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sugawara-kun is in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:00.32,sign_14271_257_Cleanup_Duty,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,650)}Cleanup Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:59.40,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sometimes, we chat a little these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning up by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.29,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:13.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:14.84,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Cleanup duty, Suga-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Practice is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:18.80,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to keep you\Nfrom club practice, Sugawara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:22.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.65,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he so eager to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:30.03,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's a clean freak?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.69,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Do you help with cleaning often?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:37.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really, but, like, since you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.74,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.56,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something he doesn't want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.87,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Am I doing a crappy job of cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll shut up and get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:47.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:51.85,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did she figure out how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:54.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just so you know,\NI didn't mean that in a weird way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if I made you uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, sorry I didn't notice, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're helping me because \Nyou noticed me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:14.98,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:18.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I never learned about this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've never learned, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:24.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like, what do you want to do, Takano?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get better at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Better? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:32.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like, so that I can clean up better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're pretty enough as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wanted to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:43.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe I'm rushing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:45.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.43,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, am I going too slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm really hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you know how I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you how you feel next time—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:02.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll learn to clean quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:04.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a topic that's easy to bring up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,About cleaning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:14.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.64,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Romantic Comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.97,sign_17927_322_Romantic_Comedy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,1)}Romantic Comedy
